transcription.speaker: Speaker 1
transcription.text: Hi, this is Sarah from Marketing. I'm having trouble connecting to the network printer.

transcription.speaker: Speaker 2
transcription.text: Hi Sarah, I can help you with that. Can you tell me which printer you're trying to connect to?

transcription.speaker: Speaker 1
transcription.text: Sure, it's the HP LaserJet Pro in the Marketing Department.

transcription.speaker: Speaker 2
transcription.text: Alright, are you connected to the office Wi-Fi? The printer is only accessible on that network.

transcription.speaker: Speaker 1
transcription.text: Yes, I'm connected to the office Wi-Fi.

transcription.speaker: Speaker 2
transcription.text: Okay, go to your computer's printer settings and try adding the printer manually. Select 'Add Printer' and look for the HP LaserJet Pro in the list.

transcription.speaker: Speaker 1
transcription.text: Got it. I see the printer in the list. Let me add it now.

transcription.speaker: Speaker 2
transcription.text: Great! Let me know if it connects successfully.

transcription.speaker: Speaker 1
transcription.text: It worked! Thank you so much for your help.

transcription.speaker: Speaker 2
transcription.text: You're welcome! Have a great day!
